	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002044_0001"/><!--pb/@n='134-1'-->
<lb/><p rend="center"><placeName>Hamilton</placeName> 9<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> August</p> 
<lb/><p rend="right"><space extent="1" unit="words"/>1864 </p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Hooker</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="6" unit="chars"/>I took the 
<lb/>liberty of addressing 
<lb/>a box to your care 
<lb/>for our friend 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Young</persName> of 
<lb/><placeName>Limefield - West - 
<lb/>Calder Mid Lothian.</placeName>
<lb/>It contains the 
<lb/>crania of two 
<lb/>Hippopotami 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002044_0002"/><!--pb/@n='134a-2'-->
<lb/>some bulbs and 
<lb/>two small tusks - 
<lb/>the bulbs especially 
<lb/>one small species 
<lb/>might be interesting 
<lb/>to you and I shall 
<lb/><del type="overwritten"><gap extent="1" unit="words" agent="illegible"/></del><add place="over-text">feel</add> obliged if 
<lb/>you send the 
<lb/>box with the 
<lb/>other things to 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Young's</persName>
<lb/>address at your 
<lb/>convenience. </p>
<lb/><p>The box came 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002044_0003"/><!--pb/@n='134a-3'-->
<lb/>by the <term type="boat">H. M. S. Narcissus</term>
<lb/>and when I heard 
<lb/>of it a few days 
<lb/>ago was in the 
<lb/>Custom House at
<lb/><placeName>Portsmouth</placeName>. </p>
<lb/><p>I hope that 
<lb/>your family and 
<lb/>your Father are 
<lb/>well &amp; beg to 
<lb/>be kindly remembered 
<lb/>to them until I can 
<lb/>go out &amp; pay my 
<lb/>respects in person<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I shall do so though 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002044_0004"/><!--pb/@n='134-4'-->
<lb/>I suppose you are 
<lb/>more frequently 
<lb/>bored by vagrants 
<lb/>than you relish<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
